# Template for local `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in a real
# key locally. NEVER commit .dev.vars or a real key. In production this is a wrangler secret:
#   wrangler secret put ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="<your-anthropic-api-key>"
# EVM private key hex for PoL DataItem signing (devnet: throwaway, faucet-funded).
# Production: wrangler secret put IRYS_UPLOAD_KEY
IRYS_UPLOAD_KEY="<evm-private-key-hex>"
